===== On the OMS servrer
[oracle@oracleem ~]$ /u01/app/oracle/oemmw/bin/emctltatus oms -details
--- List the host target
[oracle@oracleem ~]$ /u01/app/oracle/oemmw/bin/emcli get_targets -targets="host"
--- Remove the Agent Target
[oracle@oracleem ~]$ /u01/app/oracle/oemmw/bin/emcli delete_target -name="dgfpdbdc01.dgf.gov.bd:3872" -type="oracle_emd" -delete_monitored_targets
----delete the duplicate host target if needed:
[oracle@oracleem ~]$ /u01/app/oracle/oemmw/bin/emcli delete_target -name="dgfpdbdc01.dgf.gov.bd" -type="host" -force


